<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 16:09:20 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列军队公布了在加沙地面行动中丧生的另外三名士兵的姓名</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-releases-names-of-three-additional-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-ground-operation/0000018b-ed28-d4f0-affb-efeb9b140000</link><description>这三人是在过去 24 小时内坠落的，他们被确认为伞兵中士。伊农·塔米尔和参谋中士。 Dvir Barazani 和 Givati 特种作战部队成员参谋军士。埃坦·迪尚</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 15:28:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-releases-names-of-three-additional-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-ground-operation/0000018b-ed28-d4f0-affb-efeb9b140000</guid></item><item><title>拜登“重振”巴勒斯坦权力机构的愿景不足以确保加沙的未来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/bidens-vision-of-a-revitalized-pa-isnt-enough-to-secure-gazas-future/0000018b-ebdc-d6b8-a5ab-effe47300000</link><description>美国总统希望看到约旦河西岸和加沙地带建立一个统一的巴勒斯坦政府，有朝一日可能实现两国解决方案。但他在这一点上与内塔尼亚胡存在严重分歧，如果拜登从言语转向行动，分歧可能会加深</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 15:02:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/bidens-vision-of-a-revitalized-pa-isnt-enough-to-secure-gazas-future/0000018b-ebdc-d6b8-a5ab-effe47300000</guid></item><item><title>以色列为忽视以色列国防军观察员付出了代价，这个以女性为主的单位在 10 月 7 日遭受重创</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-20/ty-article/israel-pays-the-price-for-neglecting-idf-spotters/0000018b-eccb-d6b8-a5ab-ecebcf630000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 14:28:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-20/ty-article/israel-pays-the-price-for-neglecting-idf-spotters/0000018b-eccb-d6b8-a5ab-ecebcf630000</guid></item><item><title>以色列劫持哈马斯网站，将其变成 10 月 7 日暴行的展示</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/israelis-hijack-hamas-com-turning-it-into-a-display-of-october-7-atrocities/0000018b-eca2-d8b1-a9df-ecef8b380000</link><description>该网站上的一个柜台自豪地宣称 1,400 名“犹太复国主义平民被谋杀”，41 名“犹太复国主义儿童和婴儿被谋杀和活活烧死”。该网站似乎没有链接到哈马斯，其实际网站 Hamas.ps 目前似乎处于离线状态</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 13:32:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/israelis-hijack-hamas-com-turning-it-into-a-display-of-october-7-atrocities/0000018b-eca2-d8b1-a9df-ecef8b380000</guid></item><item><title>随着战争的激烈，以色列定居者和士兵试图阻止巴勒斯坦橄榄收获</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/as-war-rages-israeli-settlers-and-soldiers-try-to-block-the-palestinian-olive-harvest/0000018b-ec28-d36e-a3cb-fc7ffc280000</link><description>随着针对巴勒斯坦农民的暴力事件在这方面加剧，像贝扎莱尔·斯莫特里奇这样的极右翼政客已与西岸定居者联手参与竞选活动</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 13:02:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/as-war-rages-israeli-settlers-and-soldiers-try-to-block-the-palestinian-olive-harvest/0000018b-ec28-d36e-a3cb-fc7ffc280000</guid></item><item><title>过去的人质危机告诉我们以色列人质的未来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/what-hostage-crises-of-the-past-teach-us-about-israeli-hostages-future/0000018b-ec4c-d32d-abdb-ee4fcb980000</link><description>几十年来，以色列拒绝就释放人质进行谈判。这种情况在 20 世纪 80 年代发生了变化，随后遭到绑架的以色列人家属发起了大规模的公众压力。但这正中巴勒斯坦恐怖组织的下怀吗？连专家也不同意</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 12:00:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/what-hostage-crises-of-the-past-teach-us-about-israeli-hostages-future/0000018b-ec4c-d32d-abdb-ee4fcb980000</guid></item><item><title>国际奥斯维辛委员会要求“立即无条件”释放人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/international-auschwitz-council-demands-immediate-and-unconditional-release-of-hostages/0000018b-ec5e-d36e-a3cb-fc5fe9d40000</link><description>国际奥斯威辛委员会表示与以色列“坚定不移的声援”，并呼吁“立即无条件释放”人质，作为“制止可怕的死亡螺旋的重要第一步”</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 11:41:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/international-auschwitz-council-demands-immediate-and-unconditional-release-of-hostages/0000018b-ec5e-d36e-a3cb-fc5fe9d40000</guid></item><item><title>“谈论生命，而不是死亡”：以色列人质家属恳求政府放弃恐怖分子死刑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/talk-life-not-death-israeli-hostage-families-beg-govt-to-drop-terrorist-death-penalty/0000018b-ec3c-d6b8-a5ab-ec7e96300000</link><description>尽管哈马斯战争中在加沙被扣为人质的人的家人含泪恳求，内塔尼亚胡的极右翼伙伴仍坚持举行法律辩论</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 10:41:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/talk-life-not-death-israeli-hostage-families-beg-govt-to-drop-terrorist-death-penalty/0000018b-ec3c-d6b8-a5ab-ec7e96300000</guid></item><item><title>悲伤重聚：我们从未想过哈马斯有一天会摧毁我们的基布兹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/we-were-a-class-of-13-kibbutz-kids-we-never-could-imagine-this-would-happen/0000018b-e7ca-d05f-a5eb-e7ea55580000</link><description>哈马斯 10 月 7 日袭击的后果：我们出生于 1972 年，在后来被哈马斯摧毁的基布兹共同生活后就分道扬镳了。这就是发生在我儿时朋友身上的事</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 10:32:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/we-were-a-class-of-13-kibbutz-kids-we-never-could-imagine-this-would-happen/0000018b-e7ca-d05f-a5eb-e7ea55580000</guid></item><item><title>随着反犹太主义的加剧，英国犹太人询问他们在英国是否有未来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-20/ty-article-opinion/.premium/with-antisemitism-spiking-uk-jews-ask-if-they-have-a-future-in-britain/0000018b-e7a1-d963-a1bb-f7fbede00000</link><description>在英国，我们面临着世界上最糟糕的情况：伊斯兰极端主义反犹太主义与对美国批判种族理论和后殖民罪恶感的简单化解释相结合。自哈马斯发动袭击以来，犹太人仇恨情绪高涨 — — 并且缺乏盟友</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 09:51:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-20/ty-article-opinion/.premium/with-antisemitism-spiking-uk-jews-ask-if-they-have-a-future-in-britain/0000018b-e7a1-d963-a1bb-f7fbede00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列反对党提议修改民族国家法，增加“平等条款”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/israeli-opposition-party-proposes-amending-nation-state-law-with-equality-clause/0000018b-ebbf-d6b8-a5ab-efffca0a0000</link><description>虽然利库德集团尚未表示是否愿意支持一项修正案，但它已提出了一项关于德鲁兹人的基本法，可能是为了阻止这样的修正案，因为德鲁兹人士兵在战斗中的死亡再次引发了关于准“德鲁兹人”的争论。民族国家宪法法</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 09:47:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/israeli-opposition-party-proposes-amending-nation-state-law-with-equality-clause/0000018b-ebbf-d6b8-a5ab-efffca0a0000</guid></item><item><title>25 年前，加沙国际机场开业。随后发生了第二次起义</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-11-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/25-years-ago-gaza-intl-airport-opened-then-came-the-second-intifada/0000018b-e6fd-dffa-adef-e6fd35a10000</link><description>美国总统首次登陆加沙，巴勒斯坦国家航空公司飞往中东各国首都，加沙人开始梦想独立。但随后爆发了战斗，该场被轰炸，此后被洗劫并拆除</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 07:31:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-11-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/25-years-ago-gaza-intl-airport-opened-then-came-the-second-intifada/0000018b-e6fd-dffa-adef-e6fd35a10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军：三架无人机袭击北部军事基地附近，检测到从黎巴嫩发射了 25 架无人机</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article-live/idf-shows-footage-of-hostages-inside-al-shifa-says-soldier-was-taken-there-and-killed/0000018b-eb5e-d32d-abdb-ef5fb0370000</link><description>哈马斯扣押的人质家属恳求政府不要立法对恐怖分子判处死刑 ■ 以色列国防军公布在加沙战斗中丧生的另一名士兵的姓名 ■ 15 枚导弹落在以色列北部城镇附近 ■ 近东救济工程处：加沙流离失所者人数达到约 170 万 ■卡塔尔总理称人质协议面临的挑战“非常小” ■ 自10 月7 日以来，至少有1,200 名平民和士兵被杀； 236 名人质在加沙被扣押 ■ 哈马斯控制的卫生部：12,300 人死亡</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 06:34:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article-live/idf-shows-footage-of-hostages-inside-al-shifa-says-soldier-was-taken-there-and-killed/0000018b-eb5e-d32d-abdb-ef5fb0370000</guid></item><item><title>以色列认为哈马斯领导人辛瓦尔不理智，使人质交易变得更加紧迫</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/yemens-houthis-are-taking-aim-at-israel-for-iran/0000018b-e962-d6b8-a5ab-ed6a298a0000</link><description>尽管加沙地带北部仍然存在军事目标，但以色列需要权衡持续地面进攻的好处。 ■ 美国对与伊朗直接对抗持谨慎态度，但胡塞武装袭击的增加可能会迫使其采取行动</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 04:14:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/yemens-houthis-are-taking-aim-at-israel-for-iran/0000018b-e962-d6b8-a5ab-ed6a298a0000</guid></item><item><title>许多以色列人和巴勒斯坦人已经“清醒过来”。我拒绝做同样的事</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-20/ty-article-opinion/.premium/many-israelis-and-palestinians-have-sobered-up-i-refuse-to-do-the-same/0000018b-e90b-d32d-abdb-ef4bbc910000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 02:51:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-20/ty-article-opinion/.premium/many-israelis-and-palestinians-have-sobered-up-i-refuse-to-do-the-same/0000018b-e90b-d32d-abdb-ef4bbc910000</guid></item><item><title>以色列陆军研究：自地面入侵开始以来加沙火箭袭击次数减少</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/army-study-rocket-attacks-down-since-start-of-ground-invasion/0000018b-e939-d32d-abdb-ef7b70b00000</link><description>这一下降之所以引人注目，是因为与之前在加沙地带的行动相比，在当前的战斗中，以色列国防军并未优先考虑定位火箭弹或阻止袭击</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 02:48:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/army-study-rocket-attacks-down-since-start-of-ground-invasion/0000018b-e939-d32d-abdb-ef7b70b00000</guid></item><item><title>“另一种恐惧”：10 月 7 日之后阿拉伯人和犹太人共存的脆弱性</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-19/ty-article/.highlight/a-different-kind-of-fear-the-fragility-of-arab-jewish-coexistence-after-october-7/0000018b-e8a3-d32d-abdb-eee3db6e0000</link><description>加沙战争已经过去六周了，对 2021 年 5 月犹太和阿拉伯公民之间骚乱的报复并未实现。这片黑暗中唯一的一丝善意的背后是什么？</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 21:21:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-19/ty-article/.highlight/a-different-kind-of-fear-the-fragility-of-arab-jewish-coexistence-after-october-7/0000018b-e8a3-d32d-abdb-eee3db6e0000</guid></item><item><title>纽约市长指责教授在城市校园里营造了针对犹太人的仇恨氛围</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/new-york-mayor-blames-professors-for-hateful-atmosphere-against-jews-on-city-campuses/0000018b-e94b-d36e-a3cb-f95f9e6c0000</link><description>市长埃里克·亚当斯 (Eric Adams) 在曼哈顿中央犹太教堂告诉会众，校园已“成为仇恨的避风港”</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 20:59:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/new-york-mayor-blames-professors-for-hateful-atmosphere-against-jews-on-city-campuses/0000018b-e94b-d36e-a3cb-f95f9e6c0000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日，以色列军队公布了加沙 Al-Shifa 医院内人质的录像</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/israeli-army-releases-footage-of-hostages-inside-gazas-al-shifa-hospital-on-oct-7/0000018b-e93d-d36e-a3cb-f97f56bb0000</link><description>此外，以色列军方发言人丹尼尔·哈加里表示，被绑架并带入加沙地带的士兵诺亚·马西亚诺先被带到Al-Shifa医院附近的一处藏身处公寓，随后又被带入医院，并在那里被谋杀。病理报告证实</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 20:29:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/israeli-army-releases-footage-of-hostages-inside-gazas-al-shifa-hospital-on-oct-7/0000018b-e93d-d36e-a3cb-f97f56bb0000</guid></item><item><title>将加沙交给多国部队是一个幻想</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/multinational-force-just-a-bypass-around-the-palestinian-authority/0000018b-e8ae-d6b8-a5ab-ecee5d580000</link><description>战争结束后，阿拉伯国家拒绝向加沙派遣军队，而内塔尼亚胡则排除了巴勒斯坦权力机构控制该地区的可能性。但由非阿拉伯多国部队掌权的想法毫无意义</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 20:06:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/multinational-force-just-a-bypass-around-the-palestinian-authority/0000018b-e8ae-d6b8-a5ab-ecee5d580000</guid></item></channel></rss>